    <element name="Grandstander" id="ID_DNDC1_RING_GRANDSTANDER" source="DnDCustomContent - Campaign One" type="Magic Item">
        <description>
            <p>
                <em>You can only do so much pretending before you become the thing you're pretending to be</em>
            </p>
            <p/>
            <p>
                This ring has 3 charges, and it fully recharges when the sun rises. 
                While wearing the ring, you can expend one charge to cast 
                <em>Cheerful Song,Friends, Glimmer, Prestidigitation</em> 
                or
                <em>Thaumaturgy</em>;
                 or expend 3 charges to cast
                <em>Loki's Gift, Unearthly Chorus </em>
                or 
                <em>Guest of Honor.</em> 
                When applicable, spell cast through this ring have a spell save DC of 13.
            </p>
            <div class="reference">
